Nigerian Workers’ Body to Picket Union Bank, Trust Reports

-- B y   P a u l   O k o l o
-- 
2011-02-11T09:19:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-11/nigerian-workers-body-to-picket-union-bank-trust-reports.html
Nigeria’s main labor union
federation will start picketing branches of Union Bank of  Nigeria  Plc from Feb. 14 for banning workers from joining an
affiliate of the association,  Daily Trust  reported.  The  Nigeria Labour Congress  will implement the action in
line with a decision taken at a meeting on Feb. 4, the Abuja-
based newspaper said, citing its President Abdulwaheed Omar.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Paul Okolo in Abuja 
 pokolo@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net . 